00:00:00,182 --> 00:00:03,632
You're a fool for traveling alone,
so completely unprepared.

2
00:00:03,932 --> 00:00:06,982
You're lucky your blood's still flowing.

3
00:00:07,432 --> 00:00:08,482
Thank you.

4
00:00:09,682 --> 00:00:11,182
So...

5
00:00:11,582 --> 00:00:15,982
What brings you to
the land of the gatekeepers?

6
00:00:17,182 --> 00:00:19,682
I'm searching for someone.

7
00:00:20,182 --> 00:00:24,382
Someone very dear?
A kindred spirit?

8
00:00:25,582 --> 00:00:27,182
A dragon.
